title: Agrometal
overview: A comedy TV series set in the wild countryside. To save his marriage, Lukyn decides to take part in an amateur band competition, in which he wins a beautiful motorbike. When he succeeds, he takes his wife out on the motorbike and she will surely forgive him for everything. In short, a perfect plan! What does it matter that Lukyn doesn't have a band and that he can't really play anything...
